description:
UH HUH. THAT’S RIGHT. DA-DING DONG, HONEYS. Your Culturistas are BACK and they're spreading the GOSPEL OF CULTURE in the NEW YEAR! Joined by the incomparable Henry Koperski (@HenryKoperski), your hosts swan dive right into the cultural and political events of the week. Topics include Henry meeting Michelle Obama, thoughts on how to maintain your sanity amidst the current political shitstorm, Bullet Journaling, Norbit vs. The Klumps, Janet Jackson, Timeless Culture Stoppers, and much much more.
